dc_title_s: Linn County, Iowa, 1970, aerial photomosaic index
dc_description_s: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet labels. Images are photoreductions of mosaics created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol FT. Form of individual image numbering: FT-1LL-[number] FT-2LL-[number] or FT-3LL-[number]. Year Flown 1970. Flown by Park Aerial Surveys Inc. Louisville, K.Y. Approximate scale, 1:20,000|Contact the Map Collection at The University of Iowa Libraries: http://www.lib.uiowa.edu/maps/contact/|Scanned at 300 ppi in Greyscale.
